  "text": "We have already shown that in HL-60 cells VDR expression is transcriptionally regulated and decreases as cell growth is inhibited by PMA [CITATION_1] . In the present study, we found that in this cell line both VDR and c-myc mRNA expression seem to be directly related to cell proliferation, in agreement with the findings of Manolagas et al. [CITATION_2] , who reported that VDR and c-myc expression varies in a parallel fashion in mouse skin fibroblasts.",
